Class Admin

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Profile
      • model.Admin

  • public class Admin
extends Profile
    Represents an administrator user in the system, extending the base Profile class. This class contains administrator-specific attributes and functionality, including access to administrative accounts and privileged operations. Administrators have additional security features and access rights compared to regular users, allowing them to manage system-wide operations and user accounts.
